MultiChoice Nigeria, has announced a special discount offer tagged, Biggie Goals, on its DStv and GOtv decoders starting Thursday, 1 July 2021. The discount sees the DStv HD decoder, dish kit and one month Compact package subscription dropping by nearly 50 percent while GOtv decoder, GOtenna with one month Max package subscription dropped by about 30%. The discounted DStv and GOtv decoder offer started on Thursdayand is for a limited time only. Chief Customer Officer, MultiChoice Nigeria, Martin Mabutho, explained that the Biggie Goals offer is a way of widening access to quality entertainment programming at very affordable rates. “There is a lot to look forward to in the coming months. The sixth edition of the highly anticipated show, Big Brother Naija, premiering in July and the New Football Season which kicks off mid-August.” The DStv Compact package gives customers access to over 135 channels while the GOtv Max package provides customers with maximum entertainment on over 75 channels with local, international, sports and kiddies content. Customers can also look forward to amazing content on the platform such as the ongoing Euro 2020 tournament, the upcoming 2020 Summer Olympics, the highly anticipated Big Brother Naija season 6 show and the 2021/22 football season.